	//    - `data:` - Base64 encoded data URIs (e.g., `data:image/jpeg;base64,...`)
	//    - `http://` / `https://` - Web URLs with automatic content type detection
	//    - `file://` - Local filesystem paths
	//    - `s3://` - S3-compatible storage (format: `s3://endpoint/bucket/key`)
	//
